  "text": "Axial fittings are widely used for power generation. Their 2-4 aerodynamic blades have a horizontal axis of rotation. Nevertheless, amongst a long list of indisputable advantages, the most prominent of which is a high-efficiency rating, these plants have a significant drawback -their dependence from the wind. Not only that, but when the power is above 3 kW, these establishments require individual devices that help jump-start the machine [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
